    dc:description "FIGURES 16–21. Trichrysis tonkinensis (Mocsáry, 1914), holotype, ♀. 16. Head, mesosoma and T1, lateral view. 17. Head, frontal view. 18. Mesosoma and T1, dorsal view. 19. T2 and T3, posterior view. 20. Metasoma, dorsal view. 21. Metasoma, ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
